{"tid":596352,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國將禁止「社會信用」太低的民眾搭乘火車、飛機","createTime":"2018-03-17T14:13:02.000Z","updateTime":"2018-03-17T15:30:38.000Z","uid":37554,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"fd4d3c89dd3dd9c4134bb2d91081071ddb3be7cf","tid":596352,"uid":37554,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T14:13:02.000Z","msg":"中華人民共和國國家發展和改革委員會近日公布聲明，5月1日起，中國將禁止在該國「社會信用系統」中排名落後者，在一年內購買飛機票或火車票。<br />\n<br />\n中國政府將利用此社會信用系統為人民評分，評分內容包含犯罪紀錄、金融犯罪等，甚至還會紀錄民眾購買的東西、曾說過的話和曾做過的事。分數低的市民將會遭到處罰，也會面臨各項限制。中國計劃在2020年推出完整版的系統，但現已開始實施一些早期措施。截至目前，中國已透過此系統對逾700萬人祭出處罰。<br />\n<br />\n社會信用系統也面臨不透明的爭議：人民可能因為把腳踏車停在人行道、或道歉時不夠有誠意等小事就遭到處罰，而且事先都不會知道自己是否已被列入黑名單，更別提是否擁有追索權。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://pgw.udn.com.tw/gw/photo.php?u=https://uc.udn.com.tw/photo/2018/03/17/realtime/4578588.jpg&amp;x=0&amp;y=0&amp;sw=0&amp;sh=0&amp;sl=W&amp;fw=1050&amp;exp=3600\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fpgw.udn.com.tw%2Fgw%2Fphoto.php%3Fu%3Dhttps%3A%2F%2Fuc.udn.com.tw%2Fphoto%2F2018%2F03%2F17%2Frealtime%2F4578588.jpg%26x%3D0%26y%3D0%26sw%3D0%26sh%3D0%26sl%3DW%26fw%3D1050%26exp%3D3600&h=5a8a8340&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://udn.com/news/story/6811/3036888\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fudn.com%2Fnews%2Fstory%2F6811%2F3036888&d=Yauu6nwW8lo3geADvX2JgjQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=3162f296\" target=\"_blank\">https://udn.com/news/story/6811/3036888</a>"},{"pid":"c2be8a88c9907f397c64bdd03bb87a32424df2dd","tid":596352,"uid":34103,"like":1,"dislike":9,"score":-8,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T14:13:58.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"0a6ef3d4bce7188d5c0aa83bd65e1a3667f0a867","tid":596352,"uid":145817,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T14:14:17.000Z","msg":"預言神劇black mirror"},{"pid":"1f98d7d5b75ca1cd710a877241407a03b9c460f7","tid":596352,"uid":85751,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"0a6ef3d4bce7188d5c0aa83bd65e1a3667f0a867","tid":596352,"uid":145817,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T14:14:17.000Z","msg":"預言神劇black mirror"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T14:15:08.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"892af7c910914db456bcc525b50c41685f58ba87","tid":596352,"uid":68745,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T14:15:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"587f2dd2088032b0c2df907ce5b37ed6e6c11b50","tid":596352,"uid":85659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"892af7c910914db456bcc525b50c41685f58ba87","tid":596352,"uid":68745,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T14:15:25.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T15:00:28.000Z","msg":"白list is must<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bb818714e0bdf78319c687d80b606d271dc5b077","tid":596352,"uid":45213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-03-17T15:30:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>預言神劇black mirror</blockquote><br />\n分分鐘支共睇完直接抄橋"}]}